{
  "stem": "13851.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, when we come in Birkenau, and we were given like uniform.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was stripes, blue and white stripes uniforms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A few days later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- probably those people where they took the crematorium, they didn't have-- give them a chance, any numbers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't care.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the people they kept us wait-- holding out a while, they gave us a number,",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is-- we-- they put an appell, and there was somebody going through with a pen or something hitting in the numbers on the arm.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Depends-- you give an arm on this side, they put it other side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I turn around, I got my number on this side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a tattoo on my arm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's B2247.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was just cleaning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Doing the work-- there was one thing happen that there was-- people were standing and doing nothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they-- they wanted to make it a little bit-- look nicer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came out and ask for somebody's a gardener.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I thought find anything to ask for it, and I was-- I had interest in school in Poland to be doing some gardening.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We learned about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I said, I can do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And right at that time, I got a double portion of butter and double portion of bread, which was very helpful.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then when the people standing around, a lot of people-- they stepped on it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the next few days they said, if you want to take care of it, if you want to work on that, you have to take something and hit him over the head.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I-- I couldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That wasn't me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had to give up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I didn't want [INAUDIBLE] to be hitting people and [? things. ?]",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
